Name: S.T.A.C.
Description: This app effectively and objectively tracks symptoms of a concussion using the SCAT3 symptom checklist.Administer a baseline assessment prior to the beginning of a sport season or use the checklist to evaluate concussion symptoms when an injury is suspected. If an injury is sustained, track your symptom recovery using the checklist. Learn about common signs, symptoms, and return to work/play guidelines for concussion. Easy to use for anyone who is affected by a head injury including: athletes, parents, coaches, athletic trainers and the general population. The SCAT3 checklist is from the 2012 Consensus Statement on Concussion in Sport. This app was created and is supported by the Brain Injury Research Program at the Medical College of Wisconsin and the UW-Milwaukee App Brewery.

Name: No Butts
Description: Quitting smoking is hard - we get it. Whether youre trying to quit for the first time or youve been down this road before, the most important thing is to keep trying! And it wouldnt hurt to have some help along the way. Thats where No Butts comes in. No Butts was created by the California Smokers Helpline, a stop smoking service and research-based program at the University of California, San Diego. The Helpline has been helping smokers quit since 1992, using clinically proven methods.  We also understand that youre a busy person who may need help while on the go. The following features will help you prepare to quit, and stay quit, with strategies you can get right from the palm of your hand.1. My Plan - Tell us a little about yourself.  Answer a few, simple questions so we can get to know you better. Once youre done, No Butts will create a stop smoking plan just for you. 2. Log - Keep track of your triggers.  This can help you understand your smoking behavior better. It will also help you with your stop smoking plan. Logging your triggers can get you ready to deal with those times when you most want to light up.3. Dashboard - The dashboard offers a quick view of how youre doing, as well as important reminders. This includes your main reason to quit smoking and how many days its been since you quit.  Youll see this each time you open the app. Youll also learn about positive changes happening to your body after quitting. And youll get a summary of all triggers that you entered in the Log together with helpful strategies. 4. Quit Tools - Youll find a lot of helpful things in this section. You can read about the different quitting aids available, see checklists to get you ready for your quit date, and click on links to resources that you may find helpful.  Be sure to check these and the many other useful tidbits in this section.
Keywords: No Butts, University of California, San Diego (Business Affairs), Health & Fitness, Lifestyle, ios apps, app, appstore, app store, iphone, ipad, ipod touch, itouch, itunes

Name: Planmeca iRomexis
Description: Please note that Planmeca iRomexis development has been discontinued and it will not run on iOS 11. Please consider using Planmeca mRomexis instead. Planmeca iRomexis is a dental imaging tool, which displays images acquired with Planmeca dental equipment and stored using the Planmeca Romexis desktop software. It supports all modalities acquired with Planmeca imaging equipment, including intraoral, panoramic, cephalometric and 3D CBVT X-ray images, as well as 3D facial photos.Please note that Planmeca iRomexis development has been discontinued. Planmeca will provide compatibility updates for new Apple iOS versions until further notice. Meanwhile, please consider upgrading to Planmeca mRomexis for constantly added new features and functionalities to support new ways of working at your dental office.Planmeca iRomexis features:         Simple and powerful interface         Search and list all patients and images on the Planmeca Romexis server* on a local network (*not included, Planmeca Romexis server version 2.6.0.R or later required)         View, zoom and measure any Planmeca 2D and 3D image as single images or stacks         True hardware accelerated 3D viewing of Planmeca ProFace 3D photos and 3D surface renderings, including zooming and free rotation         Adjust the brightness and contrast of images         Capture snapshots to your camera roll for later reference or sending via e-mailYou can access all patients and images with a few taps when on the same local network as your clinics Planmeca Romexis server. A username and password are required to use the Planmeca Romexis server.  Accessed images can be stored to your devices internal memory for viewing at a time when no connection to the Planmeca Romexis server is available.INTENDED USEThe Planmeca iRomexis mobile image viewing application is intended for informational and patient education purposes only. This software is not to be used for diagnosis of images.Planmeca Romexis desktop softwareThe Planmeca Romexis desktop software is an dental imaging suite that supports both MS Windows and Apple Mac OS, and includes processing of all dental imaging modalities: intraoral, panoramic, cephalometric and  CBVT X-ray images, as well as digital dental models, 3D photos and intraoral images. For more information about the Planmeca Romexis desktop software, please visit: http://romexis.planmeca.com/
